{"word":"Stoning","slug":"stoning","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Stoning</b> Capital punishment by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=13'>Exo 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=13&verse=10'>Deu 13:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=5'>Deu 17:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=21'>Deu 22:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=37'>Heb 11:37</a><br/> Instances of stoning:<br/> - Sabbath breaker<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=36'>Num 15:36</a> <br/> - Achan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=25'>Jos 7:25</a> <br/> - Naboth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=13'>1Ki 21:13</a> <br/> - Stephen<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=59'>Act 7:59</a> <br/> - Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=19'>Act 14:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=25'>2Co 11:25</a><br/><a href='S:Witness'>Witness</a> "}]}